            {
              "question": "After precipitation has occurred, what is the relationship between IP and Ksp in the remaining solution?",
              "answer": "The remaining solution is saturated, so IP = Ksp."
            },
            {
              "question": "What key phrases suggest that IP = Ksp should be applied?",
              "answer": "solubility, saturated solution, before it begins to precipitate, and mixture after precipitation."
